reviewText: You will have to consider all the issues writers include in their episodes to be controversial and thought provoking. I love these cartoons. Not as crass as South park cartoons but just right !
summary: please please more squids on dvd. So intelligent in its reversal of intellect . Just got through watching again on adult swim.
Title: Squidbillies: Volume 1-4

reviewText: I had only seen a few episodes on TV and liked them so much that I just had to buy this set. Was not disappointed!  The humor is raw and nasty.  For adults only, not a kids cartoon.  So glad I bought it!
Title: Squidbillies: Volume 1-4

reviewText: Although Sex, Violence, and absurdity are what people are mostly stimulated by, Squidbillies does a great job (as do most Adult Swim Series') in pointing social stereotypes, class inequalities and presents them in a very creative and very funny way. This show is absolutely crazy, but I love it !
summary: One of the best Shows on Adult Swim and on T.V. in General !
Title: Squidbillies: Volume 1-4

reviewText: Fans of the TV show will love this collection of the 1st through 4th years of the program...Characters develop and get funnier as the series progesses
Title: Squidbillies: Volume 1-4

reviewText: I don't quite get the humor but my husband loves it.  He stays up late to watch it and having the whole series he can enjoy it anytime he is in the mood.
